metadata.name: Inner Workings - Self Growth
metadata.description:
Deep within, a spark ignites
A yearning to grow and take flight
To shed the old and embrace the new
And unlock the mysteries within you

It starts with a seed, a tiny thought
That blooms into something you never thought
A new perspective, a different view
A transformation of the old into something new

With each step you take, you grow and learn
Your inner workings begin to turn
And though the road may not be straight
You keep moving forward, no time to wait

The journey to self-growth is never done
But with each step, a new adventure has begun
So embrace the changes, both big and small
And watch as you become your best self of all.
